  "description": "Figure-eight's symmetric matrix creates mirror-image pulsing — left and right sides of the stereo field pulse at exactly opposite phase at 1.5 Hz. Entrainment at 0.5 half-locks the voices. The result is a breathing stereo pulse that's uniquely phase-coherent: as one side swells, the other swells in exact sympathy.",
